## Technical Implementation

### Docker Configuration:
```yaml
private-data-analyst:
  container_name: sutazai-private-data
  build: ./agents/private-data
  network_mode: none  # Air-gapped
  environment:
    - PRIVATEGPT_MODE=offline
    - ENABLE_GPU=true
    - MAX_WORKERS=4
  volumes:
    - ./private_data:/data:ro
    - ./private_models:/models
    - encrypted_storage:/secure
  security_opt:
    - no-new-privileges:true
  cap_drop:
    - ALL
```

### Privacy Configuration:
```json
{
  "privacy_config": {
    "mode": "offline_only",
    "data_retention": {
      "default_days": 30,
      "audit_logs": 365,
      "encrypted": true
    },
    "anonymization": {
      "pii_detection": true,
      "auto_redact": true,
      "hash_identifiers": true
    },
    "compliance": {
      "gdpr": true,
      "hipaa": true,
      "ccpa": true,
      "audit_enabled": true
    }
  }
}
```

